{{Top|canon=Great flood}}
The '''Great Flood''' was the end of a [[Planet/Legends|planet]]-wide ice age on the planet [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]], occurring in [[19,000 BBY]]. When the [[Water/Legends|ice]] melted, the water levels rose tremendously and submerged most of the world underwater. It also led to endless storms, and it sank multiple [[City/Legends|cities]] underwater. The [[Kaminoan/Legends|Kaminoans]] were only able to survive because of their supreme knowledge of [[Bioengineering/Legends|genetics]]. They then started living to great ages, and few knew about Kamino.

